Notes:  about Jdbc 
-------------------------------------------------------------------
step1: step1 load the driver class 

Class.forName("com.mysql.cj.jdbc.Driver");
		
---------------------------------------------------------------------
step2:  create the connection
String url = "jdbc:mysql://localhost:3306/techment?autoReconnect=true&useSSL=false";
String id = "root";
String password ="root"; 

Connection con = DriverManager.getConnection(url, id, password);
-------------------------------------------------------------------
step3:  prepare statements or statement
Statement: it is used for static query
Prepare statement: it is  used for dynamic query it is also known as parametrized query

-------------------------------------------------------------------
Step:4 execute the query
boolean execute();  (sql)(insert,update,delete)
int updateExecute(); ()
ResultSets queryExecute()  //for retrive purpose
-------------------------------------------------------------------
CRUD
C: Create
R: Retrive
U: Update
D: Delete

